          <title>
            <string language="en">Independent assortment of homologous chromosomes</string>
            <string language="x-mt-de">Unabhängige Zusammenstellung der 
übereinstimmenden Chromosomen</string>
            <string language="x-mt-fr">Assortiment indépendant des chromosomes 
homologues</string>
            <string language="x-mt-pt">Variedade independente de chromosomes homologous</string>
            <string language="x-mt-it">Assortimento indipendente dei cromosomi omologhi</string>
            <string language="x-mt-el">Ανεξάρτητη κατάταξη των ομόλογων χρωμοσωμάτων</string>
            <string language="x-mt-es">Surtido independiente de cromosomas homólogos</string>
          </title>
          <description>
            <string language="en">This diagram demonstrates independent assortment of homologous chromosomes during meiosis I resulting in the formation of four types of gametes.</string>
          </description>
          <language>x-none</language>
          <structure>
            <source>structureValues</source>
            <value>atomic</value>
          </structure>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-de">Dieses Diagramm zeigt unabhängige 
Zusammenstellung der übereinstimmenden Chromosomen während Meiosis 
I, resultierend in der Anordnung von vier Typen gametes.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-fr">Ce diagramme démontre l'assortiment indépendant
des chromosomes homologues pendant la méiose I ayant pour résultat 
la formation de quatre types de gametes.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-pt">Este diagrama demonstra a variedade independente 
de chromosomes homologous durante o meiosis I tendo por resultado a 
formação de quatro tipos de gametes.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-it">Questo schema dimostra l'assortimento 
indipendente dei cromosomi omologhi durante la meiosi I con 
conseguente formazione di quattro tipi di gametes.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-el">Αυτό το διάγραμμα καταδεικνύει την ανεξάρτητη 
κατάταξη των ομόλογων χρωμοσωμάτων κατά τη διάρκεια meiosis Ι 
με συνέπεια το σχηματισμό τεσσάρων τύπων γαμετών.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-es">Este diagrama demuestra el surtido independiente de 
cromosomas homólogos durante la meiosis I dando por resultado la 
formación de cuatro tipos de gametes.</string>
          </description>
